{"tid":1643294,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"76人Vs廣州籃球賽 美國人權組織派撐香港T恤","createTime":"2019-10-10T05:23:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T05:58:27.000Z","uid":227801,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f567faa864ae2d1be5b6527e15a5c4ef2a931144","tid":1643294,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T05:23:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20191010/60136899?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR0TI5WnTAnsWpLdhPlqvCcaAXPn2NPw0g25Cdr6_doAe8HWBi7Dr7llz60\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191010%2F60136899%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR0TI5WnTAnsWpLdhPlqvCcaAXPn2NPw0g25Cdr6_doAe8HWBi7Dr7llz60&d=N3SWmacea4shigR4hA2EmyZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=204cbc39\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191010%2F60136899%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR0TI5WnTAnsWpLdhPlqvCcaAXPn2NPw0g25Cdr6_doAe8HWBi7Dr7llz60&h=12f06c04\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20191010/60136899?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR0TI5WnTAnsWpLdhPlqvCcaAXPn2NPw0g25Cdr6_doAe8HWBi7Dr7llz60</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191010/large/1570675999_1576.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191010%2Flarge%2F1570675999_1576.jpg&h=174ec5f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國NBA籃球隊侯斯頓火箭總經理莫利（Daryl Morey），早前於Twitter發帖文撐香港「反送中」運動，引發中方不滿，其後NBA總裁施華亦撐莫利有言論自由，掀起內地抵制NBA 風波。NBA球隊費城76人周二（8日）晚主場與廣州龍獅友賽時，除了有球迷舉起寫上「FREE HONG KONG」的標語外，有人權組織在場館門口送T恤撐香港。<br />\n<br />\n美國共產主義受難者基金會周三宣佈，他們當晚在華盛頓第一資本競技館(Capital One Arena)的入口處發放1,000件印有「光復香港，時代革命」的T恤。<br />\n<br />\n昨日上海市體育總會宣佈，當晚的NBA中國季前賽「球迷之夜」被取消；而今晚湖人隊與網隊的比賽原定7點舉行，但外界並不知道這場賽事會否取消？<br />\n自由亞洲電台"},{"pid":"2932fcdb3b17be2ba69279c9b4500fba81a9a182","tid":1643294,"uid":88366,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T05:28:10.000Z","msg":"美國共產主義受難者基金會<br />\n個名中point到<br />\n香港人自動成為會員得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e525d828e82a0b5f4d835d33d36d092cf5652714","tid":1643294,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T05:29:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6da7b67741d005fc7c64e021c962a14ff990aee","tid":1643294,"uid":228868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T05:31:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c223cfe75e2bff3e26a6b6f4eb9eeb315c834c7","tid":1643294,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2932fcdb3b17be2ba69279c9b4500fba81a9a182","tid":1643294,"uid":88366,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T05:28:10.000Z","msg":"美國共產主義受難者基金會<br />\n個名中point到<br />\n香港人自動成為會員得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T05:32:57.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ccca98a95491d03a9bcde289ee5cee813b701c6f","tid":1643294,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T05:43:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fee6e1fe0ecbc9face65a8952db1f0cfdf02e102","tid":1643294,"uid":160662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T05:45:59.000Z","msg":"呢場波打左啦, 有個鬼佬係場舉牌都俾人請走左啦"},{"pid":"14da19e7629d963c6272e7507784894866c1d923","tid":1643294,"uid":191812,"like":0,"dislike":